Description
-----------
This is a python library to fast simulation some well-know mobility models:
- Random Walk
- Random Waypoint
- Random Direction
- Truncated Levy Walk
Dependencies: NumPy and Matplotlib

Contributing
------------
If you have a Github account please fork the repository,
create a topic branch, and commit your changes.
Then submit a pull request from that branch.

